videos.headline: Air Force RB goes airborne on hurdle
videos.description: Air Force RB Kadin Remsberg takes a pitch and leaps in the air to evade a tackle.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Air Force RB goes airborne on hurdle) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stoner dives into end zone for Air Force go-ahead TD
videos.description: RB Joshua Stoner scores from five yards out to give Air Force a 17-13 lead over Army early in the fourth quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stoner dives into end zone for Air Force go-ahead TD) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Air Force seals win with 4th-down stop in red zone
videos.description: On fourth-and-goal from the five-yard line, Air Force forces an Army incompletion to clinch a 17-13 win.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Air Force seals win with 4th-down stop in red zone) 2019/11/02 ESHEET
